Ghandy, well, stop writing. I don`t think you will. Ghandy's opinion has turned out not being very platform-based. Lars 'Sobi' may continue write in PC-mags. About computers or nostalgic Amiga talk. I just hope he doesn`t plan to start an online-magazine inside diskmag.de. please no!

